  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "\r\nWhen I run `npm init` it scaffolds all the solifity and js files but no package.json...\r\n\r\nthis is very bizarre to me... packages that may need to be installed need a package.json file.\r\n\r\nwhy is there no package.json scaffolded with the project?\r\n\r\nanother advantage of this is that you can prefill some common npm commands...\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"scripts\": {\r\n    \"start\": \"truffle develop\",\r\n    \"test\": \"truffle test\"\r\n  },\r\n```",
